description: Two new rookies join the ranks of NK fighters this week. Today's match pits Zach Alexander against Tucker Scott in a battle for sexual domination. The stakes are high because the winner today will leave with a perfect record and each fighter is anxious to prove they have what it takes. Zach's fighting style is balls out aggression. He can hardly contain his raging hard on from the very first round. Tucker has experience fighting his older brothers, and knows how to handle a bully. Tucker is faster. He plans on letting this meathead tire himself out and goes for the kill. Today's match reeks masculine aggression and sexual humiliation.
title: Tucker Scott vs. Zach Alexander
